          h2 Hardware content
          p Intelliscope hardware consists of a dry electrode-based ECG add-on and a low powered control unit which can be easily integrated with a traditional stethoscope. Integrating these two components with an existing stethoscope will transform it to a wireless stethoscope with the ability to record synchronized high quality PCG and ECG signals and with a powerful AI backend. The ECG add-on is carefully designed with a unique shape, making it very easy to use with a stethoscope and also as a separate hand-held device. The battery powered circuitry inside the control unit, provides filtering and active noise cancellation to the acquired signals and wirelessly transmits them to the userâ€™s mobile phone or computer; allowing the user to record, visualize and analyze the data.
